<D>__{marfa, texas, 1993.}
<B>__{credits begin.}
<A>__{a plume of dust comes into frame. the dust is from a truck, orange and white and violet, with "fedex" blazoned across the side. the truck turns into a collection of ramshackle world war ii era quonset huts and outbuildings. around the outbuildings are large sculptures of wood and metal.}
